Vang đã ký hợp đồng cung cấp hệ thống POS (Hệ thống quản lý bán hàng) cho một khu ăn uống (17 nhà hàng của Nhật Bản) trong siêu thị AEON Bình dương (Dự kiến mở cửa vào tháng 11 năm 2014).',NULL,NULL),(47,3,'trien-khai-thanh-cong-he-thong-vvpos-cho-sakura-food-court-o-aeon-binh-duong','articles','en','Triển khai thành công hệ thống VVPOS cho Sakura FoodCourt ở AEON Bình Dương','IMG_3322.jpg',NULL,'Ngày 10/11/2014, Việt Vang đã triển khai thành công hệ thống VVPOS cho khu ăn uống  (17 nhà hàng của Nhật Bản) trong siêu thị AEON Bình Dương. Với lượng khách hàng khá lớn,  VVPOS đã cung cấp hệ thống thanh toán và quản lý cho chuỗi cửa hàng này',NULL,NULL),(48,3,'trien-khai-thanh-cong-he-thong-vvpos-cho-sakura-food-court-o-aeon-binh-duong','articles','ja','Triển khai thành công hệ thống VVPOS cho Sakura FoodCourt ở AEON Bình Dương','IMG_3322.jpg',NULL,'Ngày 10/11/2014, Việt Vang đã triển khai thành công hệ thống VVPOS cho khu ăn uống  (17 nhà hàng của Nhật Bản) trong siêu thị AEON Bình Dương. Với lượng khách hàng khá lớn,  VVPOS đã cung cấp hệ thống thanh toán và quản lý cho chuỗi cửa hàng này',NULL,NULL),(49,4,'loi-chao-cua-giam-doc','articles','en','Director\'s greeting','boss-image.png',NULL,NULL,'<p>At almost all kind of  business, it is clearly that the software helps to make quicker and more accurate performance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At industrial countries, it is natural that after finishing what is called industrialization, they also made good use of IT applications. At developing countries, in order not to be left behind, the IT-ization should take place along with the industrialization.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>When we look at Vietnamese small and medium enterprises, besides some that use IT products widely and successfully, there are surprisingly large numbers of enterprises that are still STRANGE to IT applying.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fortunately, thanks to the Internet, fast and popular IT development, those companies which are late to the IT-ization, still have chance to approach newest IT technology of the world.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I graduated from a University in Japan on Computer Science major, and I worked 4 years as a System Engineer to create Systems for Kobelco Steel Company. After that, I came back to Vietnam to take over an Outsourcing IT company where we again developed software for Japan. Thanks to this valuable experience, I understand the need of using IT in business and know-how of software development, especially, by young Vietnamese engineers. This is nothing but these two keywords of [Ability to design] and [Ability to test].</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We managed to be  “A company can design”, “A company can guarantee quality”. We are taking in the newest IT technologies from the world every day and with the flexible ideas of young engineers, we propose IT solutions to you. In the end we create the best software for you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We, with following strengths, are confident to create the software for you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>– Capability of consulting and software designing －You just have to give your idea and we will make it clear and create relevant software.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>– High quality －We have gone all the way to satisfy even strict Japanese customers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>– Capability to meet the Deadline －We know that this is the basic condition to get customers’ satisfaction.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>By above philosophy, we established this VietVang JSC in October, 2012.</p>',NULL),(50,4,'loi-chao-cua-giam-doc','articles','ja','社長の挨拶','boss-image.png',NULL,NULL,'<p>ほとんどの業務において、ソフトウエアを使えば、より早く、正確に作業ができることは言うまでもありません。<br/>\r\n世界で工業化の進んだ国は当然必然的にIT分野についても充実させてきました。一方、先進国から少し出遅れ、今から本格的に工業化を目指す国々（例えばベトナム）では、IT化についても平行して進めていかなければならない状況になっています。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>実際のベトナム社会を見てみると、細かいところまでITを適用できているところもあれば、全く導入していない中小企業や組織も驚くほどたくさん存在しています。\r\n幸いなことに、インターネットのおかげで、IT業界の発展と普及の速度は速く、IT化が遅れた企業でも最新の技術を取り入れられる機会があります。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>私は日本の大学の情報通信専攻を卒業し、神戸製鋼のシステムを作るシステムエンジニアとして４年間働きました。その後、ベトナムに帰って、再びオフショア開発部門を担当しました。この貴重な経験で業務へのシステム（IT）導入の必要性を理解し、システム開発のノーハウ、特に若いベトナム人のエンジニアによって開発するノーハウも理解しました。それはやはり「設計能力」と「検証能力」という２つのキーワードに尽きます。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>弊社は、「ソフトウエアの設計ができる会社」、「ソフトウエアの品質検証ができる会社」を目指しました。世界中の最新IT技術を日夜学習し、自らの若さによる能動的なアイディアでお客様にシステムのイメージをご提案させていただき、最後まで高品質な製品（システム）を提供いたします。弊社は下記の強みを持ちソフトウエアを提供している。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>– コンサル及びソフトウエア設計ができる － 顧客の要望を伺い、弊社は顧客にコンサルティングし、ソフトウエアを完成させる。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>– 高品質 － 弊社は日本の中でも特に品質に厳しい企業にも満足していただいている。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>– 納期厳守を努力する － 顧客に満足いただけるよう、スケジュール通りに納品することを努力する。</p>\r\n<p>以上のことを目指し、2012年10月に弊社、VietVang JSC　（ベトバン株式会社）を設立いたしました。</p>',NULL),(51,5,'thong-tin-cong-ty','articles','en','Company overview',NULL,NULL,NULL,'<tr>\r\n	<th>Found date</th>\r\n        <td>31/10/2012</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n        <th>Tax code</th>\r\n        <td>0312032889</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n        <th>Capital</th>\r\n        <td>4,5 Billion VND (Nearly 220.000 USD)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n        <th>Employees</th>\r\n        <td>13 people ( February 2015)</td>\r\n</tr>',NULL),(52,5,'thong-tin-cong-ty','articles','ja','会社概要',NULL,NULL,NULL,'<tr>\r\n	<th>設立日</th>\r\n        <td>31/10/2012</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n        <th>会社のコード</th>\r\n        <td>0312032889</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n        <th>資本金</th>\r\n        <td>45億 VND （約 1,500 万円）</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n        <th>社員数</th>\r\n        <td>13人 (2015年2月)</td>\r\n</tr>',NULL),(53,6,'cong-cu-su-dung','articles','en','Tools to use',NULL,NULL,NULL,'<tr>\r\n	<th width=\"180\">\r\n		<p align=\"center\"><b>Work</b></p>\r\n	</th>\r\n	<th width=\"238\">\r\n		<p align=\"center\"><b>Tools to use</b></p>\r\n	</th>\r\n	<th width=\"228\">\r\n		<p align=\"center\"><b>Remark</b></p>\r\n	</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td width=\"180\">Progress Management</td>\r\n	<td width=\"238\">Microsoft Project Management</td>\r\n	<td width=\"228\"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td width=\"180\">Screen Design</td>\r\n	<td width=\"238\">Balsamiq Mockups<br>Visual Studio 2010<br>Word</td>\r\n	<td width=\"228\">Just take 2,3 days to propose the Design</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td width=\"180\">Database Design</td>\r\n	<td width=\"238\">CASE Studio 2<br>Rational Rose<br>PowerDesigner</td>\r\n	<td width=\"228\"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td width=\"180\">Develop Environment</td>\r\n	<td width=\"238\">Eclipse<br>phpDesigner<br>Visual Studio 2010<br>Net Bean</td>\r\n	<td width=\"228\"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td width=\"180\">Coding</td>\r\n	<td width=\"238\">PHP<br>Java<br>.Net (C#, ASP.Net,WinForm,…)<br>Android<br>iOS</td>\r\n	<td width=\"228\"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td width=\"180\">Source code management</td>\r\n	<td width=\"238\">Subversion (SVN)</td>\r\n	<td rowspan=\"3\" width=\"228\">- Hosted by VietVang.<br>\r\n		– Secured.<br>\r\n		– Permission on each user.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td width=\"180\">Bugs management</td>\r\n	<td width=\"238\"><a href=\"http://113.161.80.250:89/mantisbt/login_page.php\">Mantis Bugtracker</a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td width=\"180\">Test server</td>\r\n	<td width=\"238\">HTTPS</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td width=\"180\">Communication Language</td>\r\n	<td width=\"238\">Vietnamese<br>\r\n		Japanese<br>\r\n		English</td>\r\n	<td width=\"228\">1 kyu level.</td>\r\n</tr>',NULL),(54,6,'cong-cu-su-dung','articles','ja','使用するツール',NULL,NULL,NULL,'<tr>\r\n	<th width=\"180\">\r\n		<p align=\"center\"><b>仕事</b></p>\r\n	</th>\r\n	<th width=\"238\">\r\n		<p align=\"center\"><b>使用するツール</b></p>\r\n	</th>\r\n	<th width=\"228\">\r\n		<p align=\"center\"><b>備考</b></p>\r\n	</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td width=\"180\">進捗管理</td>\r\n	<td width=\"238\">マイクロソフト プロジェクト マネジメント</td>\r\n	<td width=\"228\"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td width=\"180\">画面設計</td>\r\n	<td width=\"238\">Balsamiq Mockups<br>Visual Studio 2010<br>Word</td>\r\n	<td width=\"228\">２、３日でシステムのイメージを設計し、提案できる。</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td width=\"180\">データベース設計</td>\r\n	<td width=\"238\">CASE Studio 2<br>Rational Rose<br>PowerDesigner</td>\r\n	<td width=\"228\"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td width=\"180\">開発環境</td>\r\n	<td width=\"238\">Eclipse<br>phpDesigner<br>Visual Studio 2010<br>Net Bean</td>\r\n	<td width=\"228\"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td width=\"180\">コーディング</td>\r\n	<td width=\"238\">PHP<br>Java<br>.Net (C#, ASP.Net,WinForm,…)<br>Android<br>iOS</td>\r\n	<td width=\"228\"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td width=\"180\">ソースコード管理</td>\r\n	<td width=\"238\">Subversion (SVN)</td>\r\n	<td rowspan=\"3\" width=\"228\">- VietVangでホストする。<br>\r\n		– セキュリティ的に安心。<br>\r\n		– 顧客のアクセスを許可できる。</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td width=\"180\">不具合管理</td>\r\n	<td width=\"238\"><a href=\"http://113.161.80.250:89/mantisbt/login_page.php\">Mantis Bugtracker</a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td width=\"180\">テストサーバ</td>\r\n	<td width=\"238\">HTTPS</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n	<td width=\"180\">コミュニケーション言語</td>\r\n	<td width=\"238\">ベトナム語<br>\r\n		日本語<br>\r\n		英語</td>\r\n	<td width=\"228\">一級レベル</td>\r\n</tr>',NULL),(55,7,'mo-hinh-hoat-dong','articles','en','Working process',NULL,NULL,NULL,'<br/>\r\n	<p>A software development project consists of following steps.</p>\r\n	<p>[Requirement]<br>\r\n	-> [Basic Design]<br>\r\n	-> [Detail Design]<br>\r\n	-> [Coding]<br>\r\n	-> [Review Source Code]<br>\r\n	-> [Unit Test]<br>\r\n	-> [Integrated Test]<br>\r\n	-> [Running Test]</p>\r\n	<p>The characteristics of each step and the difference when working with VietVang (comparing to when working with normal IT company) are as below.</p>\r\n	<table class=\"info-company\">\r\n		<tbody>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<th style=\"vertical-align: middle;\" rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"3\" width=\"290\">\r\n					<p align=\"center\"><strong>Work Task</strong></p>\r\n				</th>\r\n				<th style=\"vertical-align: middle;\" rowspan=\"2\">\r\n					<p align=\"center\"><strong>Task Prerequisite</strong></p>\r\n				</th>\r\n				<th style=\"vertical-align: middle;\" colspan=\"2\">\r\n					<p align=\"center\"><strong>Who is in charge?</strong></p>\r\n				</th>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style=\"vertical-align: middle;\">\r\n					<p align=\"center\"><strong>when working with normal IT company</strong></p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style=\"vertical-align: middle;\">\r\n					<p align=\"center\"><strong>when working with VietVang</strong></p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style=\"vertical-align: middle;\">\r\n				<td width=\"87\">\r\n					<p align=\"center\">Requirement</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td width=\"71\">\r\n					<p align=\"center\">&lt;–&gt;</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td width=\"131\">\r\n					<p align=\"center\">Running Test</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<p align=\"center\">Understand the target of the software</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<p align=\"center\"><span class=\"label label-success\">Customer</span></p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<p align=\"center\"><span class=\"label label-success\">Customer</span></p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style=\"vertical-align: middle;\">\r\n				<td width=\"87\">\r\n					<p align=\"center\">Basic Design</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td width=\"71\">\r\n					<p align=\"center\">&lt;–&gt;</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td width=\"131\">\r\n					<p align=\"center\">Integrated Test</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<p align=\"center\">Understand how the software should function</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<p align=\"center\"><span class=\"label label-success\">Customer</span></p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<p align=\"center\"><strong><span class=\"label label-success\">Customer</span>&nbsp;&amp;<em>Viet Vang</em></strong></p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style=\"vertical-align: middle;\">\r\n				<td width=\"87\">\r\n					<p align=\"center\">Detail Design</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td width=\"71\">\r\n					<p align=\"center\">&lt;–&gt;</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td width=\"131\">\r\n					<p align=\"center\">Unit Test</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<p align=\"center\">Understand how the software should be created</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<p align=\"center\"><strong><span class=\"label label-success\">Customer</span>&nbsp;&amp;&nbsp;<em>IT company</em></strong></p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<p align=\"center\"><em><strong>Viet Vang</strong></em></p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style=\"vertical-align: middle;\">\r\n				<td width=\"87\">\r\n					<p align=\"center\">Coding</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td width=\"71\">\r\n					<p align=\"center\">&lt;–&gt;</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td width=\"131\">\r\n					<p align=\"center\">Review Source Code</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<p align=\"center\">Understand how to create (develop) the software</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<p align=\"center\"><em><strong>IT company</strong></em></p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<p align=\"center\"><em><strong>Viet Vang</strong></em></p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</tbody>\r\n	</table>\r\n	<br/>\r\n	<p>It is clear that you do not have to work that much when working with VietVang. It means you can <span class=\"label label-important\">save a lot of overhead task</span>. </p>',NULL),(56,7,'mo-hinh-hoat-dong','articles','ja','業務プロセス',NULL,NULL,NULL,'<br/>\r\n<p>ソフトウエアの開発案件には基本的に次のステップがある。</p>\r\n<p>[要求]<br>\r\n-> [基本設計]<br>\r\n-> [詳細設計]<br>\r\n-> [コーディング]<br>\r\n-> [ソースコードレビュー]<br>\r\n-> [単体テスト]<br>\r\n-> [結合テスト]<br>\r\n-> [運用テスト]</p>\r\n<p>各ステップの特徴及び弊社と仕事をする場合の特徴（他社との違い）は下記に記す</p>\r\n<table class=\"info-company\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style=\"vertical-align: middle;\" rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"3\" width=\"290\">\r\n				<p align=\"center\"><strong>仕事の項目</strong></p>\r\n			</th>\r\n			<th style=\"vertical-align: middle;\" rowspan=\"2\">\r\n				<p align=\"center\"><strong>仕事の要求</strong></p>\r\n			</th>\r\n			<th style=\"vertical-align: middle;\" colspan=\"2\">\r\n				<p align=\"center\"><strong>対応仕事の当事者</strong></p>\r\n			</th>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"vertical-align: middle;\">\r\n				<p align=\"center\"><strong>通常のIT会社と仕事する場合</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"vertical-align: middle;\">\r\n				<p align=\"center\"><strong>VietVangと仕事する場合</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr style=\"vertical-align: middle;\">\r\n			<td width=\"87\">\r\n				<p align=\"center\">要求</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td width=\"71\">\r\n				<p align=\"center\">&lt;–&gt;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td width=\"131\">\r\n				<p align=\"center\">運用テスト</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				<p align=\"center\">該当ソフトウエアへの需要が分かる</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				<p align=\"center\"><span class=\"label label-success\">顧客</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				<p align=\"center\"><span class=\"label label-success\">顧客</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr style=\"vertical-align: middle;\">\r\n			<td width=\"87\">\r\n				<p align=\"center\">基本設計</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td width=\"71\">\r\n				<p align=\"center\">&lt;–&gt;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td width=\"131\">\r\n				<p align=\"center\">結合テスト</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				<p align=\"center\">該当ソフトウエアの仕様が分かる</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				<p align=\"center\"><span class=\"label label-success\">顧客</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				<p align=\"center\"><strong><span class=\"label label-success\">顧客</span>&nbsp;&amp;<em>Viet Vang</em></strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr style=\"vertical-align: middle;\">\r\n			<td width=\"87\">\r\n				<p align=\"center\">詳細設計</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td width=\"71\">\r\n				<p align=\"center\">&lt;–&gt;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td width=\"131\">\r\n				<p align=\"center\">単体テスト</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				<p align=\"center\">該当ソフトウエアの開発方法が分かる</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				<p align=\"center\"><strong><span class=\"label label-success\">顧客</span>&nbsp;&amp;&nbsp;<em>IT会社</em></strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				<p align=\"center\"><em><strong>Viet Vang</strong></em></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr style=\"vertical-align: middle;\">\r\n			<td width=\"87\">\r\n				<p align=\"center\">コーディング</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td width=\"71\">\r\n				<p align=\"center\">&lt;–&gt;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td width=\"131\">\r\n				<p align=\"center\">ソースコードレビュー</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				<p align=\"center\">現在のIT技術を活かして、該当のソフトウエアを開発する</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				<p align=\"center\"><em><strong>IT会社</strong></em></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				<p align=\"center\"><em><strong>Viet Vang</strong></em></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br/>\r\n<p>通常のIT会社と比べると、弊社と仕事をする場合、顧客はプロジェクトを完成させるのにかかる手間が省ける。、つまり顧客 の <span class=\"label label-important\">オーバーヘッド</span>がより少なくなる。 </p>',NULL),(57,8,'qua-trinh-dao-tao-nhan-su','articles','en','Resource education',NULL,NULL,NULL,'<br/>\r\n<p>Với khách hàng, slogan của Việt vang là [<strong>Sự thỏa mãn của khách hàng là mục tiêu của chúng tôi</strong>],</p>\r\n<br/>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">\r\n	<a href=\"images/logo-1.png\">\r\n		<img class=\"size-full wp-image-165 aligncenter\" src=\"images/logo-1.png\" width=\"620\" height=\"140\">\r\n	</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<br/>\r\n<p>và để thực hiện điều này thì sau mỗi dự án chúng tôi đều điều tra mức độ thỏa mãn của khách hàng &nbsp;qua phiếu điều tra [Customer Satisfaction Servey] để rút kinh nghiệm cho các dự án sau.</p>\r\n<br/>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">\r\n	<a href=\"images/hinhanh.png\">\r\n		<img class=\"size-full wp-image-166 aligncenter\" src=\"images/hinhanh.png\" width=\"620\" height=\"140\">\r\n	</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<br/>\r\n<p>Trong nội bộ&nbsp;công ty Việt vang áp dụng slogan [Triệt để Báo Cáo - Liên Lạc - Thảo Luận]. Tất cả các vấn đều đều được đưa ra thảo luận mổ xẻ để giải quyết. Các nhân viên được đào tào bài bản về Cách báo cáo, thời điểm cần báo cáo, có các mẫu tài liệu chuẩn để nhân viên báo cáo.</p>\r\n<br/>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">\r\n	<a href=\"images/sonhanvien.png\">\r\n		<img class=\"size-full wp-image-167 aligncenter\" src=\"images/sonhanvien.png\" width=\"418\" height=\"262\">\r\n	</a>\r\n</p>\r\n',NULL),(58,8,'qua-trinh-dao-tao-nhan-su','articles','ja','人材教育',NULL,NULL,NULL,'<br/>\r\n<p>Với khách hàng, slogan của Việt vang là [<strong>Sự thỏa mãn của khách hàng là mục tiêu của chúng tôi</strong>],</p>\r\n<br/>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">\r\n	<a href=\"images/logo-1.png\">\r\n		<img class=\"size-full wp-image-165 aligncenter\" src=\"images/logo-1.png\" width=\"620\" height=\"140\">\r\n	</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<br/>\r\n<p>và để thực hiện điều này thì sau mỗi dự án chúng tôi đều điều tra mức độ thỏa mãn của khách hàng &nbsp;qua phiếu điều tra [Customer Satisfaction Servey] để rút kinh nghiệm cho các dự án sau.</p>\r\n<br/>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">\r\n	<a href=\"images/hinhanh.png\">\r\n		<img class=\"size-full wp-image-166 aligncenter\" src=\"images/hinhanh.png\" width=\"620\" height=\"140\">\r\n	</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<br/>\r\n<p>Trong nội bộ&nbsp;công ty Việt vang áp dụng slogan [Triệt để Báo Cáo - Liên Lạc - Thảo Luận]. Tất cả các vấn đều đều được đưa ra thảo luận mổ xẻ để giải quyết. Các nhân viên được đào tào bài bản về Cách báo cáo, thời điểm cần báo cáo, có các mẫu tài liệu chuẩn để nhân viên báo cáo.</p>\r\n<br/>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">\r\n	<a href=\"images/sonhanvien.png\">\r\n		<img class=\"size-full wp-image-167 aligncenter\" src=\"images/sonhanvien.png\" width=\"418\" height=\"262\">\r\n	</a>\r\n</p>\r\n',NULL),(59,1,'he-thong-thanh-toan-vv-pos','products','en','VV-POS System','product-title-image.png',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(60,1,'he-thong-thanh-toan-vv-pos','products','ja',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(61,9,'danh-cho-nhan-vien','articles','en','Recruitment',NULL,NULL,NULL,'<ul>\r\n	<li><a href=\"http://115.79.201.33:89/MonthlyReport/public/login\"><img src=\"images/add-icon.png\">Quản lý nội bộ</a></li>\r\n        <li><a href=\"http://webmail.vietvang.net\"><img src=\"images/add-icon.png\">Webmail</a></li>\r\n</ul>',NULL),(62,9,'danh-cho-nhan-vien','articles','ja','募集',NULL,NULL,NULL,'<ul>\r\n	<li><a href=\"http://115.79.201.33:89/MonthlyReport/public/login\"><img src=\"images/add-icon.png\">Quản lý nội bộ</a></li>\r\n        <li><a href=\"http://webmail.vietvang.net\"><img src=\"images/add-icon.png\">Webmail</a></li>\r\n</ul>',NULL);

